Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  珊迪奇克斯要出远门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sandy Cheeks is going out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.57,0:01:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她临走前交代海绵宝宝和派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and has asked SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮她照顾宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to do a little pet-sitting for her
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照顾宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pet-sitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,924)\fs60}坐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样不会把宠物伤着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't that hurt them?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许珊迪本来应该另外找人照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she should have asked someone else
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我都不知道你会说鸟语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Patrick, I didn't know you spoke bird
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.71,0:01:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是意大利语  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's Italian, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了各位  这边的是小鸟的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boys, this here's Birdy's food
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天要喂两次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feed him twice a day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要喂一整袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This whole sack?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  喂一杯就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Naw, just a cup's worth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.60,0:01:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是我的蟋蟀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's my cricket
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟋蟀在向你们问好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's saying hello to you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't he cute?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不会意大利语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't speak Italian
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这个是小蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, and this here's Snakey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肚子里肿起来那块是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that lump in his belly?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是人家晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's his dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  交代得够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几天过后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you fellers in a couple of days
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.02,0:01:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘介绍这个宠物了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:01:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot about this pet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我唯一养的小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's only Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃得不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He don't eat much
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看小青虫  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he great?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, little fella
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挠我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kitchy-kitchy koo-koo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是不是很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't he just precious?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把小青虫带出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's take him out to play
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.37,0:02:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,998
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,998
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,999
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,999
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,000
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏好了吗  我来找了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready or not, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You found me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He found us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.13,0:02:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友之间就要至死不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A friend is a friend to the end of the end
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's forever and a day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.95,0:02:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在你身边  我绝不与你分别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay by your side, won't hear me say goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.72,0:02:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come what may
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause that's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause that's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause that's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause that's what friends do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我好不想过完今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, SpongeBob, I don't want today to end, ever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一生中像今天这样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Days like today come once
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能就只有一两天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe twice in a lifetime
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,细细品味每一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Savor every moment
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要感谢小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's all thanks to Wormy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,680)}好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了这个送给小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made this for Wormy--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的新好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our new best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再见  新好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until tomorrow, new best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别难过  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be sad, little buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.80,0:03:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天我们一回来马上跟你嬉戏玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be back first thing in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for frolic and fun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.51,0:03:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何太阳一定要在这美好的一天落下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why must the sun set on this perfect day?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好睡吧  小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleep well, Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别难过了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be sad, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天就能再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only until tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就要玩抓人游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, and then we're going to play tag
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就要涂颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we're going to color
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后搭一座纸牌屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we're build a house of cards
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回来了  小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're back, Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wormy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Wormy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来应该在里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got to be in here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫很有可能出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think something bad happened to Wormy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,586)}好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还把好朋友绶带落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He left his Best Friend ribbon behind
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但不管它是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But whatever it is
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定已经把小青虫吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it must have eaten Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么老是会出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does this keep happening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧往大门逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we got to make a run for the door
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  它把我们唯一出口堵上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, he's blocking our only exit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trapped in here 
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟那个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with that, that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃好朋友的一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,best friend eater
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's not panic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要团结一致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just have to stick together
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  我们是二打一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, it's two against one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.87,0:05:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它把派大星吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's eaten Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're alive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.02,0:05:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, we can't just
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这只可怕怪物留在珊迪家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,leave this horrible monster in Sandy's house
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很有可能会吃掉珊迪其他宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It might eat Sandy's other pets
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者更惨烈  吃掉珊迪的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or worse, it might eat Sandy's pets
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  有可能会吃掉珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it might eat Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把它赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to get it out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是打给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它要接电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to answer it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子特别让人有食欲  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look pretty appetizing, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在趴在上面等怪物过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, just stay here and wait for the monster
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿网来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the net
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  网拿快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hurry up with that net
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,876)}珊迪
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真没那么好吃  怪物先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really don't taste that good, Mr. Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我过来了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  怪物先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别吃我  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please don't eat me, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧  我不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spare me, I don't taste good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪会为我们骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's going to be so proud of us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把可怕的怪物赶出她家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got that horrible monster out of her house
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好的一点就是  她宠物都安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And best of all her pets are safe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为可怕怪物现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause that horrible creature is now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直奔着蟹堡王过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,heading straight for the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它要进大门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's going in the front
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(562,398)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's use the secret entrance
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, hold still
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它要吃了章鱼哥跟蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's going to eat Squidward and Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快卧倒  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit the deck, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "money"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况现在特危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're in serious danger
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个  有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a, a
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个怪物在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a monster out there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是会花钱的客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he a paying customer?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want to eat Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只吃你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wants to eat you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟吃了小青虫一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like it ate Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wormy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was so young
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们忘不了你  小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never forget you, Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然白痴小剧场演完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if Moron Theater's over
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就来看一眼这个怪物的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just take a look at this monster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the monster?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty scary, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活生生的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A living nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have known
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要从狂人快船上下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting off the Loonie Express
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的生物你们没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, just because you swabs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never seen a creature like this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不代表它就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean it's dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们尽力警告他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We tried to warn them
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't watch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看这只可怕怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a load of the scary monster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着就人畜无害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks harmless
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有点可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of cute
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想到了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of money
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物把他们吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It ate them
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物还走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先是小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后章鱼哥  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then Squidward, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只到处飞的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That flying monster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经吃掉我们三个朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has eaten three friends too many
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须告知居民们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must inform the citizens
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶势力浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil has surfaced
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fate of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就掌握在我们手里  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is in our hands, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's roll
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这个局面特别棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is a very delicate situation
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要特别小心处理才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and must be treated with great care and sensitivity
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run, everybody, run
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有怪物逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster on the loose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.34,0:09:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:37.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(466,498)}当心
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的居民们请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只到处飞的怪物要吃了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a flying monster that's going to eat you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,816)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意  注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, attention
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只巨大怪物正在袭击裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A giant monster is attacking Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拯救了裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saved the city
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想要是我们没跟大家交代怪物的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just think what might have happened
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村会有什么后果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if we didn't tell everyone about the monster
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交代什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,712)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,758)}行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,712)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,870)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032,480)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有龙卷风刮过这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like a twister hit this place
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小青虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi there, Wormy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该得等我回来才变蝴蝶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You weren't supposed to change till I got back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就能装起来了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ought to hold you, little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪抓到怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy caught the monster
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道大家原来特别想念我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know I'd been missed so much
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Golly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我得多出几次远门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go out of town more often
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.89,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(359,390)}彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,366)\frz18.25}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.25\pos(424,684)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:54.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(424,318)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(330,336)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(516,644)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,458)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经36天没客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,36 days without a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No food
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three days
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, me bucko
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food's on the way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身上有钱  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got money, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给他上吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, bring this man some grub
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁他还没晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he keels over
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的来了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全海底最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finest under the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可活力又在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but where's the pizzazz?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟有什么主题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, what is the theme here?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水下主题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwater?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无聊透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's boring
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,water
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,atmosphere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人会来餐厅要气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody goes to a restaurant for atmosphere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要的都是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They go for food
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.67,0:13:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.63,0:13:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去蟹堡王吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to eat at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不要  去贝壳小屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, let's go to the Shell Shack
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们那边有会说话的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've got a talking dog
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.13,0:13:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说狗是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, what's a dog?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钱长脚走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money walking
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须想出那样的促销手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to think up a gimmick like that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把客人引回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get people back in here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以  女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家多多购买蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make sure you buy lots of Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在此期间我要活埋自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as I bury myself alive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不提供免费续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No free refills
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.86,0:13:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贝壳小屋那条会说话的狗唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The talking dog at the Shell Shack is singing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是找不到好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't find an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要停业了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go out of business
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么就没人能给我个好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't someone give me an idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊  我可需要点子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great Neptune in heaven, I need an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.12,0:14:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我有个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你还在等什么  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of money are you waiting for, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的蟹老板  做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Krabs, prepare yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以不用坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother sitting down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你看到这个一定会起立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you'll just stand up when you see this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的大堡礁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great Barrier Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这蟹黄堡馊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That patty's spoiled
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  那不是腐坏的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's not tainted meat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是涂了颜料的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's painted meat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡  六种设计师色彩均可购买
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties, available in six designer colors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是看着就很有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't that look appetizing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来个多加紫色的橙色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me an orange patty with extra purple
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后还有啥  亮片奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next, sequined milkshakes?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蝴蝶结薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bow-tie french fries?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.17,0:15:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡  彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties, Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这肯定是好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this is a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你们瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.67,0:15:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll, I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要自己开餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll open my own restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你也生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, are you angry, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不到我额头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see my forehead
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个好点子  别人都不认可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea and no one else thinks so
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充气裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Inflatable pants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你点子是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要开一家餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to open up a restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sell Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管我馊点子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget my dumb idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那点子好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好迎接客流高峰了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for the big rush, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就会有不少饿肚子客人大排长龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon those hungry customers will be lining up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们开业了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because we are open
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,688)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(432,520)}逝者安息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,838)}我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,882)}此处付款          彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们坐这多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, how long have we been sitting here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再画个新电池装进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to draw a new battery for this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一蟹老板说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if Mr. Krabs was right?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的点子可能确实太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe my idea is dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.34,0:16:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  有时候我们必须深入内心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, sometimes we have to go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deep inside ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to solve our problems
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scared
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我来帮你深入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going in for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充气裤子太白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stupid inflatable pants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这边卖吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you sell food here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在卖彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We sell Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意都发绿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That thing's green
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Green
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.15,0:17:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Green
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs was right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with all these?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是紫色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that one purple?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紫色可是我最爱的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Purple is my favorite color
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't half bad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, world
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡就是史上最强点子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties is the best idea ever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞克  你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rick, how could you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你我一体同心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and I, together we were one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was before
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm splitting us up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们打断这个节目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt this program
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:01.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,814)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播一则重大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for an important news announcement
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身后这一大群狂热分子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This wild throng behind me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.14,0:18:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在为裤头村的全新美食欢呼尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is screaming for Bikini Bottom's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,newest culinary sensation
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来听听看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's take a listen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不难看出  彩色汉堡十分火爆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's easy to see that Pretty Patties are popular
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可彩色汉堡究竟有什么魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But just what is it about them
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让裤头村的食客们这般狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that drives Bikini Bottom feeders wild?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们很搭我们的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They match our purses
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们让我想起了家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They remind me of home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties rule
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是如何走向成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how do you explain all this success?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.68,0:18:39.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么笨一个点子怎么就赚得到钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:39.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you make money with such a stupid idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么强一个点子怎么就赚不到钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how can you not make money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with such a brilliant idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起先我们不知道要怎么处理那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At first we didn't know what to do with all the money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们试过把钱埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We tried burying it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shredding it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and burning it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后我们决定把钱送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But in the end, we decided to just give it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:59.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,386)}免费送钱
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come again, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就再排一次队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting back in line
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要亲眼去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to see this for meself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不稀罕你有多想吃彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care how much you want your Pretty Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正你都得跟我们一样排队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to have wait in line like the rest of us
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没人来这排队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never had a line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,308)}服务号数
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是46853号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's number 46,853?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没有46853个客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never had 46,853 customers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐给你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要色彩缤纷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stay pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩色汉堡太火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pretty patties are a big hit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实挺火  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They sure are, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现十分出色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing pretty well for yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.10,0:19:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计你已经把蟹堡王抛在脑后了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you've completely forgotten the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  从来没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sir, I haven't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, sometimes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.34,0:19:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的特想念蟹堡王的往日时光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really miss the old days at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定也很想念章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you miss Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the crow's nest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我最想念什么不  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what I miss the most, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿两片腌椰菜摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tiny squeaky sound you get
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发出来的小小的吱吱声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you rub two pickles together
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我意思吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.28,0:20:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都懂  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yes, I do, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王只要走一小段路就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the Krusty Krab is only a short walk away
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看在老交情份上  你就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head on down for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不能走  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't leave, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摊子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the stand?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摊子我来帮你照看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll watch the stand for ye
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有更好的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a better idea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.37,0:20:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这个路边摊直接归我管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take this old roadside stand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off your hands for keeps
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in exchange
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把蟹堡王交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有章鱼哥  有烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with Squidward, the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有吱吱叫的腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all those squeaky pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹堡王的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the key to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她现在是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's yours now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.79,0:20:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我该干啥  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should I do now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑过去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run to her, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就在等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's waiting for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我腿麻了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't feel my legs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子你放心  我来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, lad, I'll fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上帮这位去蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get this to the Krusty Krab on the double
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美梦成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dreams do come true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,428)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在由我为大家售卖彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty Patties is now under new management
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.05,0:21:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for me money
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎购买彩色汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Pretty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我收你钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your money?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我们退钱  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want a refund, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.47,0:22:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.62,0:22:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的破烂彩色汉堡害我脸变紫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your dumb Pretty Patties turned my face purple
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我苏格兰短裙里面成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what I got under my kilt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看我们的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look at our tongues
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want our money back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.08,0:22:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退给我们46853个客人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All 46,853 of us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.39,0:22:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.14,0:22:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My key
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钥匙哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my key?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.66,0:22:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.55,0:22:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  放我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, let me in
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.65,0:22:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.38,0:22:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  放我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, let me in
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
